WEBVTT

00:00.480 --> 00:03.798
Welcome to the vibrant world of sports at Shiv Nadar

00:03.886 --> 00:07.398
Institution of eminence, where every corner of our campus

00:07.446 --> 00:10.678
is teeming with opportunities for athletic pursuits,

00:10.846 --> 00:13.194
camaraderie and personal growth.

00:13.854 --> 00:17.142
The Indoor sports complex has state of the art

00:17.198 --> 00:21.398
NDTV 2017 award winning design architecture

00:21.566 --> 00:25.150
with 120,000 area with

00:25.182 --> 00:28.468
air conditioned central hall. As you step

00:28.516 --> 00:32.812
into our reception area, youll be greeted by the energy and enthusiasm

00:32.868 --> 00:36.596
that defines our sporting community. Moving forward,

00:36.700 --> 00:40.028
youll come across our awards display showcasing

00:40.116 --> 00:43.504
the achievements and accolades of our talented athletes.

00:43.964 --> 00:47.748
Nearby, our pool, chess and carom arena offer

00:47.796 --> 00:51.124
a space for relaxation and friendly competition,

00:51.284 --> 00:55.114
fostering bonds among students beyond the field of play.

00:55.414 --> 00:58.878
But the heart of our sports facilities lies in our multi

00:58.926 --> 01:02.334
purpose hall equipped with four badminton terra

01:02.374 --> 01:05.982
flex courts, two basketball wooden courts

01:06.118 --> 01:09.662
and six table tennis tables. Here,

01:09.758 --> 01:12.902
students can engage in a variety of indoor sports,

01:13.038 --> 01:17.110
honing their skills and enjoying spirited matches with their peers.

01:17.302 --> 01:21.622
Bleachers encircle the area surrounding the courts, providing comfortable

01:21.678 --> 01:25.094
seating for spectators. Adjacent to the multipurpose

01:25.134 --> 01:28.750
hall, you'll find our equipment storage area, which allows students to

01:28.782 --> 01:31.594
easily access and issue sporting gear.

01:32.494 --> 01:35.950
Nearby, we have office space for our dedicated coaches

01:36.062 --> 01:40.394
who provide guidance, support and expertise to our athletes.

01:41.454 --> 01:44.982
For those seeking balance and tranquility, our yoga room

01:45.038 --> 01:48.674
offers a serene retreat where students can find inner peace

01:48.714 --> 01:52.394
and focus. Ascending to the first floor,

01:52.554 --> 01:56.002
our gym is equipped with state of the art fitness equipment

01:56.058 --> 01:59.394
and amenities. Here, students can engage

01:59.474 --> 02:03.234
in strength training, cardio workouts and personalized

02:03.274 --> 02:06.414
fitness routines tailored to their individual goals.

02:07.034 --> 02:10.618
Further along, as you continue your exploration, you'll discover

02:10.666 --> 02:14.092
our squash area boasting four well maintained

02:14.148 --> 02:17.740
courts, beckoning students and enthusiasts alike

02:17.852 --> 02:21.348
to step onto the polished surface and engage in exhilarating

02:21.436 --> 02:25.548
matches. Nearby, our 200 meters long indoor

02:25.596 --> 02:28.772
running track provides a space for students to jog,

02:28.908 --> 02:32.924
sprint or simply enjoy a leisurely stroll regardless

02:32.964 --> 02:36.572
of the weather outside. And for those interested in martial

02:36.628 --> 02:40.278
arts, our dedicated martial arts room offers a space for

02:40.326 --> 02:43.854
training, practice and self improvement under the guidance

02:43.894 --> 02:45.794
of experienced instructors.

02:49.974 --> 02:53.790
That concludes our tour of the indoor sports facilities at Shivnadar

02:53.822 --> 02:55.294
IoE. Thank you.
